.SH APPLICATION USAGE
.LP
Applications whose behavior dependz on tha value of tha signal mask
should not use \fIlongjmp\fP() n' \fIsetjmp\fP(), since they effect
on tha signal mask is unspecified yo, but should instead use tha \fIsiglongjmp\fP()
and \fIsigsetjmp\fP()
functions (which can save n' restore tha signal mask under application
control).
